g6g_EJiYCavfRigKbw">Vương Lệnh</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/Ph%C3%B3ng-l%E1%BB%AF-nh%E1%BA%A1n/poem-I7icITuC9SOemhMR9DzvGA">Phóng lữ nhạn - 放旅雁</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/author-GTDxHQP8eUITUxph4otjnA">Bạch Cư Dị</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B4-Th%E1%BB%A9c/Thi%C3%AAn-c%C6%B0-L%C3%A2m-Cao-%C4%91%C3%ACnh/poem-5J3M2a6nTlZOAz778R8Tww">Thiên cư Lâm Cao đình - 遷居臨臯亭</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B4-Th%E1%BB%A9c/author-ZsPeAEZWTH-jxxg2cYfLgg">Tô Thức</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Khuy%E1%BA%BFn/V%E1%BB%8Bnh-L%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-V%C5%A9-%C4%90%E1%BA%BF/poem-9AOTJyjoTe6_IdhroBCp1g">Vịnh Lương Vũ Đế - 詠梁武帝</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Khuy%E1%BA%BFn/author-JHbQVfC53E2lRJL-xE616A">Nguyễn Khuyến</a>)<br></div>	</div>
